{"tid":2070632,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"英媒：古天奴因「當初太渴望離隊」無緣重返利物浦","createTime":"2020-06-19T08:58:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-27T05:53:54.000Z","uid":165817,"like":57,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"c60662f8a8e96adedb955c1079fe21414f2537ec","tid":2070632,"uid":165817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T08:58:09.000Z","msg":"英國 The Athletic 記者占土皮雅斯報導，巴塞隆拿中場古天奴不太可能返回利物浦，因為他當時「太渴望離隊」。<br />\n<br />\n占士皮雅斯表示：「老實說，我不認為古天奴能夠回到利物浦。」<br />\n<br />\n「球迷們可能已經忘記了，他當時在球季開始前提出轉會申請的事。這件事說明了他對利物浦的態度，也展現出他是多麼渴望離隊。」<br />\n<br />\n「我認為利物浦和古天奴已經沒什麼關係了，他們現在就像一個團隊一樣，正在穩步向前。」<br />\n<br />\n「如果他真的回歸了，我絕對會感到驚訝。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aKJLstH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaKJLstH.jpg&h=5267552c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"42e73c7d698a528d94ca96236af554cdcb133711","tid":2070632,"uid":47492,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T08:59:09.000Z","msg":"抵死"},{"pid":"d27b68317f0d40074c95b4ccda576d13ec291428","tid":2070632,"uid":165817,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"42e73c7d698a528d94ca96236af554cdcb133711","tid":2070632,"uid":47492,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T08:59:09.000Z","msg":"抵死"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T08:59:59.000Z","msg":"都叫開心笑過....."},{"pid":"fac8438391c7d3fbba32fd868c5a3f26a71d03cf","tid":2070632,"uid":4661,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T09:00:25.000Z","msg":"脫北者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94b8047bad432bdff042b54ddc91c37da1a5621c","tid":2070632,"uid":30837,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T09:00:44.000Z","msg":"呢條狗閪真係"},{"pid":"a3850e0d85e68870451c958b4df38100c9e35079","tid":2070632,"uid":165817,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"quote":{"pid":"fac8438391c7d3fbba32fd868c5a3f26a71d03cf","tid":2070632,"uid":4661,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":2,"re